# OutputTransaction

A list of output transactions.
## Properties
Name | Type | Description | Notes
------------ | ------------- | ------------- | -------------
**transaction_id** | **str** | The unique identifier for the transaction. | [readonly] 
**type** | **str** | The type of the transaction e.g. &#39;Buy&#39;, &#39;Sell&#39;. The transaction type should have been pre-configured via the System Configuration API endpoint. | [readonly] 
**description** | **str** | The description of the transaction. This only exists on transactions generated by LUSID e.g. a holdings adjustment transaction. | [optional] [readonly] 
**instrument_identifiers** | **dict(str, str)** | The set of instrument identifiers that can be used to resolve the transaction to a unique instrument. | [optional] 
**instrument_uid** | **str** | The unqiue Lusid Instrument Id (LUID) of the instrument that the transaction is in. | [readonly] 
**transaction_date** | **datetime** | The date of the transaction. | [readonly] 
**settlement_date** | **datetime** | The settlement date of the transaction. | [readonly] 
**units** | **float** | The number of units transacted in the associated instrument. | [readonly] 
**transaction_amount** | **float** | The total value of the transaction in the transaction currency. | [optional] [readonly] 
**transaction_price** | [**TransactionPrice**](TransactionPrice.md) |  | [optional] 
**total_consideration** | [**CurrencyAndAmount**](CurrencyAndAmount.md) |  | [optional] 
**exchange_rate** | **float** | The exchange rate between the transaction and settlement currency. For example if the transaction currency is in USD and the settlement currency is in GBP this this the USD/GBP rate. | [optional] [readonly] 
**transaction_to_portfolio_rate** | **float** | The exchange rate between the transaction and portfolio currency. For example if the transaction currency is in USD and the portfolio currency is in GBP this this the USD/GBP rate. | [optional] [readonly] 
**transaction_currency** | **str** | The transaction currency. | [optional] [readonly] 
**properties** | [**dict(str, PerpetualProperty)**](PerpetualProperty.md) | Set of unique transaction properties and associated values to stored with the transaction. Each property will be from the &#39;Transaction&#39; domain. | [optional] [readonly] 
**counterparty_id** | **str** | The identifier for the counterparty of the transaction. | [optional] [readonly] 
**source** | **str** | The source of the transaction. This is used to look up the appropriate transaction group set in the transaction type configuration. | [optional] [readonly] 
**transaction_status** | **str** | The status of the transaction. | [optional] [readonly] 
**entry_date_time** | **datetime** | The asAt datetime that the transaction was added to LUSID. | [optional] [readonly] 
**cancel_date_time** | **datetime** | If the transaction has been cancelled, the asAt datetime that the transaction was cancelled. | [optional] [readonly] 
**realised_gain_loss** | [**list[RealisedGainLoss]**](RealisedGainLoss.md) | The collection of realised gains or losses resulting from relevant transactions e.g. a sale transaction. The cost used in calculating the realised gain or loss is determined by the accounting method defined when the transaction portfolio is created. | [optional] [readonly]
